.TH wxMouseCaptureChangedEvent 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxMouseCaptureChangedEvent \- An mouse capture changed event is sent to a window that loses its mouse capture.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
This is called even if \fIwxWindow:releaseMouse/1\fR was called by the application code. Handling this event allows an application to cater for unexpected capture releases which might otherwise confuse mouse handling code.

.PP
Only for:wxmsw

